Subject:Re: [Flexradio] Waterfall memory for each band

Ray,It's easy to do if you use DDutil.  Set up 'band change macros' with the CAT commands that set upper and lower display frequencies.  For example, ZZDQ-115; sets the lower Panadapter display frequency to -115dB.  Jim KJ2P 
